/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=fa4e6c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=6ea69012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=5fabbf1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=35b5dc7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"066bfa74ccbffaa6d2df43c453ccf9dc227e00f7","tid":1669294,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"64d740cf1c8d99212b11359bd6418452fb57b7eb","tid":1669294,"uid":319497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"一開始以為你地假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一search你地個名都知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如正正經經幫下其他候選人？"},{"pid":"64e4b29ff2767ec2704ea2c23ab4f90c457c83f5","tid":1669294,"uid":242734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"民建聯b隊，不了"},{"pid":"4fc321a0659d89a590e93a22cf74579c5a593055","tid":1669294,"uid":299947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:06:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母建制狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3fa8eec26bb540dfcec3f3c2f59dccd909375b","tid":1669294,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"842d6474f34f2e3620666249af7f09c319377